{"tid":1292691,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［又賴］8個裁判和阿根廷對着幹","createTime":"2019-07-07T12:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T12:16:03.000Z","uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7a3a948705bb3d976fcb348bd37cebb98bc24f70","tid":1292691,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:10:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AqhRE6g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAqhRE6g.jpg&h=1f70a553&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美斯爭執紅牌被逐 阿根廷挫智利奪季軍<br />\n<br />\n美斯於季軍戰只踢了36分鐘，就因為和加利美度爭執而被罰出場，但事實上當時美斯並無任何過火場動作，只是默默地受到對手用頭、用心口不斷頂撞。不過球證竟然拔出2紅，將2人齊齊趕出場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n史卡朗尼表示：「始終不明白美斯為何領紅。其實我們應該踢決賽，但取得季軍是我們唯一可做的事。我們是一個團隊，任何一位成員受到不公對待，整隊也會受到傷害，今日美斯受害，就讓我們非常不滿。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n提到VAR，史卡朗尼表示：「我們的敵人不只是對手，還有總共8個人的裁判團隊。從實際表現所見，裁判們根本不知道何謂VAR。」"},{"pid":"99ba04f7cc1c26a9b01eea2c637b8efc6a8375b1","tid":1292691,"uid":99568,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:10:58.000Z","msg":"Good morning sir"},{"pid":"85deb5f881a3c0dcc5095b3c4676fb99b7cd8388","tid":1292691,"uid":99568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:11:26.000Z","msg":"sir 返工咁得閒上連登?"},{"pid":"3b03e1a0f6ade5cfb2f3a2f0ad9d58e5a8fd6905","tid":1292691,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:12:05.000Z","msg":"好心啦，贏咗就贏咗，輸咗就輸咗。<br />\n贏撚咗場波話人哋黑哨。<br />\n算撚數啦季軍戰<br />\n<br />\n下年咪到我哋阿根廷主辦國囉，嘈乜撚嘢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"930de42fe9a8bf7792c04971aafff4c2838641dc","tid":1292691,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:14:00.000Z","msg":"我都唔明兩個互頂 兩個失曬控<br />\n紅牌有乜問題 又唔係淨係比一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我作為球王美斯忠實fans都覺得大家應該要冷靜落嚟睇清楚成件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都有唔啱大家都罰紅牌好合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1cc753bbddad7e126b033d7834849740ab28d4","tid":1292691,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:15:48.000Z","msg":"鳩sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d7dd63c212d0c8090d60e012542bf0adcc0d4e","tid":1292691,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"930de42fe9a8bf7792c04971aafff4c2838641dc","tid":1292691,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:14:00.000Z","msg":"我都唔明兩個互頂 兩個失曬控<br />\n紅牌有乜問題 又唔係淨係比一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我作為球王美斯忠實fans都覺得大家應該要冷靜落嚟睇清楚成件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都有唔啱大家都罰紅牌好合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:16:03.000Z","msg":"想同你互頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}